text: "Smells Like Nirvana" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of "Smells Like Teen Spirit" by Nirvana. It was released on the album Off the Deep End in 1992. It pokes fun at how people often cannot understand Nirvana's lyrics. Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1992 songs
title: Smells Like Nirvana
